rocketsmbd (1.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * AES-256-GCM and AES-CCM (128/256) ciphers; prefer_aes256 option.
  * Perf: send_zc buffered send, worker core pinning, opt-in SQPOLL,
    multishot accept.
  * Opt-in read-caching leases (oplocks=true). Guest+seal hang fixed.

 -- Glenn West <glennswest@neuralcloudcomputing.com>  Sun, 14 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

rocketsmbd (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * SMB3 encryption (AES-128-GCM); send_zc zero-copy buffered send path;
    worker core pinning and opt-in io_uring SQPOLL.
  * Fix: guest + SMB3 encryption (seal) no longer hangs the mount.

